{"type": "article", "id": 13712, "title": "圆形椅子", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-19T07:36:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 26, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606135115xqI7EfXe6OcMV9PD.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t圆形控们看过来，David Adjaye 新设计的这一系列椅子叫做 “Double Zero ”，椅背和椅面全部是五颜六色的圆，同时，椅子的框架系统也不像普通的椅子那样是四条腿儿，而是选择了交叉的支撑结构，加上圆形的椅背和椅面，整个椅子不管从哪个角度看过去都个性十足。<a href=\"http://www.adjaye.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看  David Adjaye 官方主页。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141422m8EQVI46YHzAK1jT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.89364303\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141423RBtsH4KgxC3vapSF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.89364303\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141423wR4j7DfU6PugkrAN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74694377\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261414242GzxfNObuS6sZEPm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74694377\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141424uM1WZTSDsBbqU4eV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.86919315\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141425gqbQAfK1uOhPZlUM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.89364303\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141425PRhvkyXoQ46j1Nqd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.89364303\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141425FwaX7G5YB4dEiVLA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.86430318\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141426jYHBvebo8sZuMnUX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.86430318\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141427ED0Z4NyIxsnAUP9B.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}